node.text:
Listed by @Kollosche_ - Welcome to Infinity Broadbeach.

Now under construction Infinity presents the best value large apartments on the market in Broadbeach, giving you the space you need, the lifestyle you want and the luxury you deserve.

Featuring large 216m2 half floor apartments and 432m2 whole floor apartments, with a wraparound balconies and views of the ocean, city skyline and the Gold Coast hinterland.

Resident facilities include a 20 metre north facing pool, generous indoor and outdoor entertaining areas, and a state-of-the-art gymnasium, all dedicated to indulgent recreation.

Walk to beautiful patrolled surf beaches, Broadbeach cafes and restaurants, Pacific Fair Shopping Centre, The Star Casino, parklands and the Light Rail transport system.

Contact @Kollosche_ for more information.

_________________
